  "text": "In the dendrogram drawn from the Nei's genetic distances [CITATION_1] , the Guarapuava and Porto Barreiro populations were the closest related, and along with the Marialva, Xanxerê, and Campos Novos populations, formed a delimited group (Fig 5) .",
